transcript:
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Hello. Ha sir, pahunch gaye?
Executive: Ji?
Customer: Main bol raha hun, pahunch gaye?
Executive: Nahi nahi nahi, thoda sa samay aur do, pahunchne wala hun.
Customer: Achcha, abhi pahunchne wale hain?
Executive: Hmm.
Customer: Chaliye, theek hai, pahunchiye.
